    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice your<strong> red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>black beans</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach </strong>and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
