    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>to the pan with your <strong>ground cumin </strong>and <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong></p><p>Cook for a further 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Tip: Add a drizzle more oil if your pan is looking a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1688467430309-x200.jpg",
