        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide 3/4 of the <strong>enchilada filling</strong> (save some for later!) between the<strong> tortillas</strong>, covering only half of each tortilla</p><p>Roll up the <strong>tortillas</strong> tightly – these are your <strong>enchiladas</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
