            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Place the <strong>enchiladas</strong> in an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>(or two!), seam side down</p><p>Top with the <strong>remaining enchilada filling</strong> and <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Put the dish[es] in the oven for 10-12 min or until the cheese is golden and melted – these are your <strong>cheesy black bean enchiladas</strong></p>",
